{"tid":2328751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"私煙的死完美突顯林鄭抗疫的失敗","createTime":"2020-12-16T17:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T22:28:09.000Z","uid":55257,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e05799749da3bb312bcdacb3c82fe71089a9b530","tid":2328751,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"私煙生前有冇做齊以下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 出入餐廳有冇scan安心出行？<br />\n2. 有冇聽從減少聚會及出行？<br />\n3. 發病個陣有冇去做病毒檢測？<br />\n<br />\n我賭J佢一樣都冇做好，連呢d傻西藍屍都唔撚理林鄭的抗疫措施，習維尼仲點會俾你林鄭上京述職？"},{"pid":"f79dbc76bb232339ec6bf2afb3791ba91c0cc3be","tid":2328751,"uid":267494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:46:01.000Z","msg":"3應該有既<br />\n不過就係咁先證明全民檢測都多鳩餘<br />\n二月錯過左塞源頭<br />\n咁多個月既經驗越黎越指向只可以考慮封城戒嚴之類<br />\n唔上唔落既社交距離<br />\n咪繼續唔上唔落攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a54beea8f1531785af5fab3e6a45687871bf3d","tid":2328751,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:43:33.000Z","msg":"檢測左點解仲會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9e93045789ea0a62a5b0dde9d7b1b618c9539b","tid":2328751,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T21:48:45.000Z","msg":"新聞講 私煙死左先話佢初步確診"},{"pid":"df3572dc92352776d92bf45781c34fbace11a3b3","tid":2328751,"uid":181651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T22:28:09.000Z","msg":"立完國安法 應該好安全"}]}